    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/SetTheory/Ordinal/FixedPointApproximants.html#OrdinalApprox.lfpApprox_ord_eq_lfp\">OrdinalApprox.lfpApprox_ord_eq_lfp</a> may also be worth mentioning as it allows for nice transfinite induction on the ordinal <code>(Order.succ (Cardinal.mk α)).ord</code>. At least that was my motivation for implementing it.</p>",
